<?php
$translation_description = "Translation: Sahih International";
$verses_translation = array(
  array('id' => '9','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'This is the Book about which there is no doubt, a guidance for those conscious of Allah -
'),
  array('id' => '19','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '12','content' => 'Unquestionably, it is they who are the corrupters, but they perceive [it] not.
'),
  array('id' => '28','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '21','content' => 'O mankind, worship your Lord, who created you and those before you, that you may become righteous -
'),
  array('id' => '32','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '25','content' => 'And give good tidings to those who believe and do righteous deeds that they will have gardens [in Paradise] beneath which rivers flow. Whenever they are provided with a provision of fruit therefrom, they will say, "This is what we were provided with before." And it is given to them in likeness. And they will have therein purified spouses, and they will abide therein eternally.
'),
  array('id' => '116','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '109','content' => 'Many of the People of the Scripture wish they could turn you back to disbelief after you have believed, out of envy from themselves [even] after the truth has become clear to them. So pardon and overlook until Allah delivers His command. Indeed, Allah is over all things competent.
'),
  array('id' => '214','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '207','content' => 'And of the people is he who sells himself, seeking means to the approval of Allah . And Allah is kind to [His] servants.
'),
  array('id' => '219','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '212','content' => 'Beautified for those who disbelieve is the life of this world, and they ridicule those who believe. But those who fear Allah are above them on the Day of Resurrection. And Allah gives provision to whom He wills without account.
'),
  array('id' => '244','chapter_number' => '2','verse_number' => '237','content' => 'And if you divorce them before you have touched them and you have already specified for them an obligation, then [give] half of what you specified - unless they forego the right or the one in whose hand is the marriage contract foregoes it. And to forego it is nearer to righteousness. And do not forget graciousness between you. Indeed Allah , of whatever you do, is Seeing.
'),
  array('id' => '376','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '83','content' => 'So is it other than the religion of Allah they desire, while to Him have submitted [all] those within the heavens and earth, willingly or by compulsion, and to Him they will be returned?
'),
  array('id' => '382','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '89','content' => 'Except for those who repent after that and correct themselves. For indeed, Allah is Forgiving and Merciful.
'),
  array('id' => '383','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '90','content' => 'Indeed, those who reject the message after their belief and then increase in disbelief - never will their [claimed] repentance be accepted, and they are the ones astray.
'),
  array('id' => '391','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '98','content' => 'Say, "O People of the Scripture, why do you disbelieve in the verses of Allah while Allah is Witness over what you do?"
'),
  array('id' => '401','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '108','content' => 'These are the verses of Allah . We recite them to you, [O Muhammad], in truth; and Allah wants no injustice to the worlds.
'),
  array('id' => '422','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '129','content' => 'And to Allah belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is on the earth. He forgives whom He wills and punishes whom He wills. And Allah is Forgiving and Merciful.
'),
  array('id' => '428','chapter_number' => '3','verse_number' => '135','content' => 'And those who, when they commit an immorality or wrong themselves [by transgression], remember Allah and seek forgiveness for their sins - and who can forgive sins except Allah ? - and [who] do not persist in what they have done while they know.
'),
  array('id' => '496','chapter_number' => '4','verse_number' => '3','content' => 'And if you fear that you will not deal justly with the orphan girls, then marry those that please you of [other] women, two or three or four. But if you fear that you will not be just, then [marry only] one or those your right hand possesses. That is more suitable that you may not incline [to injustice].
'),
  array('id' => '520','chapter_number' => '4','verse_number' => '27','content' => 'Allah wants to accept your repentance, but those who follow [their] passions want you to digress [into] a great deviation.
'),
  array('id' => '536','chapter_number' => '4','verse_number' => '43','content' => 'O you who have believed, do not approach prayer while you are intoxicated until you know what you are saying or in a state of janabah, except those passing through [a place of prayer], until you have washed [your whole body]. And if you are ill or on a journey or one of you comes from the place of relieving himself or you have contacted women and find no water, then seek clean earth and wipe over your faces and your hands [with it]. Indeed, Allah is ever Pardoning and Forgiving.
'),
  array('id' => '565','chapter_number' => '4','verse_number' => '72','content' => 'And indeed, there is among you he who lingers behind; and if disaster strikes you, he says, " Allah has favored me in that I was not present with them."
'),
  array('id' => '711','chapter_number' => '5','verse_number' => '42','content' => '[They are] avid listeners to falsehood, devourers of [what is] unlawful. So if they come to you, [O Muhammad], judge between them or turn away from them. And if you turn away from them - never will they harm you at all. And if you judge, judge between them with justice. Indeed, Allah loves those who act justly.
'),
  array('id' => '763','chapter_number' => '5','verse_number' => '94','content' => 'O you who have believed, Allah will surely test you through something of the game that your hands and spears [can] reach, that Allah may make evident those who fear Him unseen. And whoever transgresses after that - for him is a painful punishment.
'),
  array('id' => '791','chapter_number' => '6','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'It is He who created you from clay and then decreed a term and a specified time [known] to Him; then [still] you are in dispute.
'),
  array('id' => '799','chapter_number' => '6','verse_number' => '10','content' => 'And already were messengers ridiculed before you, but those who mocked them were enveloped by that which they used to ridicule.
'),
  array('id' => '847','chapter_number' => '6','verse_number' => '58','content' => 'Say, "If I had that for which you are impatient, the matter would have been decided between me and you, but Allah is most knowing of the wrongdoers."
'),
  array('id' => '863','chapter_number' => '6','verse_number' => '74','content' => 'And [mention, O Muhammad], when Abraham said to his father Azar, "Do you take idols as deities? Indeed, I see you and your people to be in manifest error."
'),
  array('id' => '923','chapter_number' => '6','verse_number' => '134','content' => 'Indeed, what you are promised is coming, and you will not cause failure [to Allah ].
'),
  array('id' => '929','chapter_number' => '6','verse_number' => '140','content' => 'Those will have lost who killed their children in foolishness without knowledge and prohibited what Allah had provided for them, inventing untruth about Allah . They have gone astray and were not [rightly] guided.
'),
  array('id' => '979','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '25','content' => 'He said, "Therein you will live, and therein you will die, and from it you will be brought forth."
'),
  array('id' => '1048','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '94','content' => 'And We sent to no city a prophet [who was denied] except that We seized its people with poverty and hardship that they might humble themselves [to Allah ].
'),
  array('id' => '1056','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '102','content' => 'And We did not find for most of them any covenant; but indeed, We found most of them defiantly disobedient.
'),
  array('id' => '1067','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '113','content' => 'And the magicians came to Pharaoh. They said, "Indeed for us is a reward if we are the predominant."
'),
  array('id' => '1085','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '131','content' => 'But when good came to them, they said, "This is ours [by right]." And if a bad [condition] struck them, they saw an evil omen in Moses and those with him. Unquestionably, their fortune is with Allah , but most of them do not know.
'),
  array('id' => '1096','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '142','content' => 'And We made an appointment with Moses for thirty nights and perfected them by [the addition of] ten; so the term of his Lord was completed as forty nights. And Moses said to his brother Aaron, "Take my place among my people, do right [by them], and do not follow the way of the corrupters."
'),
  array('id' => '1134','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '180','content' => 'And to Allah belong the best names, so invoke Him by them. And leave [the company of] those who practice deviation concerning His names. They will be recompensed for what they have been doing.
'),
  array('id' => '1146','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '192','content' => 'And the false deities are unable to [give] them help, nor can they help themselves.
'),
  array('id' => '1158','chapter_number' => '7','verse_number' => '204','content' => 'So when the Qur\'an is recited, then listen to it and pay attention that you may receive mercy.
'),
  array('id' => '1172','chapter_number' => '8','verse_number' => '12','content' => '[Remember] when your Lord inspired to the angels, "I am with you, so strengthen those who have believed. I will cast terror into the hearts of those who disbelieved, so strike [them] upon the necks and strike from them every fingertip."
'),
  array('id' => '1201','chapter_number' => '8','verse_number' => '41','content' => 'And know that anything you obtain of war booty - then indeed, for Allah is one fifth of it and for the Messenger and for [his] near relatives and the orphans, the needy, and the [stranded] traveler, if you have believed in Allah and in that which We sent down to Our Servant on the day of criterion - the day when the two armies met. And Allah , over all things, is competent.
'),
  array('id' => '1264','chapter_number' => '9','verse_number' => '29','content' => 'Fight those who do not believe in Allah or in the Last Day and who do not consider unlawful what Allah and His Messenger have made unlawful and who do not adopt the religion of truth from those who were given the Scripture - [fight] until they give the jizyah willingly while they are humbled.
'),
  array('id' => '1285','chapter_number' => '9','verse_number' => '50','content' => 'If good befalls you, it distresses them; but if disaster strikes you, they say, "We took our matter [in hand] before," and turn away while they are rejoicing.
'),
  array('id' => '1297','chapter_number' => '9','verse_number' => '62','content' => 'They swear by Allah to you [Muslims] to satisfy you. But Allah and His Messenger are more worthy for them to satisfy, if they should be believers.
'),
  array('id' => '1300','chapter_number' => '9','verse_number' => '65','content' => 'And if you ask them, they will surely say, "We were only conversing and playing." Say, "Is it Allah and His verses and His Messenger that you were mocking?"
'),
  array('id' => '1315','chapter_number' => '9','verse_number' => '80','content' => 'Ask forgiveness for them, [O Muhammad], or do not ask forgiveness for them. If you should ask forgiveness for them seventy times - never will Allah forgive them. That is because they disbelieved in Allah and His Messenger, and Allah does not guide the defiantly disobedient people.
'),
  array('id' => '1437','chapter_number' => '10','verse_number' => '73','content' => 'And they denied him, so We saved him and those with him in the ship and made them successors, and We drowned those who denied Our signs. Then see how was the end of those who were warned.
'),
  array('id' => '1552','chapter_number' => '11','verse_number' => '79','content' => 'They said, "You have already known that we have not concerning your daughters any claim, and indeed, you know what we want."
'),
  array('id' => '1579','chapter_number' => '11','verse_number' => '106','content' => 'As for those who were [destined to be] wretched, they will be in the Fire. For them therein is [violent] exhaling and inhaling.
'),
  array('id' => '1593','chapter_number' => '11','verse_number' => '120','content' => 'And each [story] We relate to you from the news of the messengers is that by which We make firm your heart. And there has come to you, in this, the truth and an instruction and a reminder for the believers.
'),
  array('id' => '1633','chapter_number' => '12','verse_number' => '37','content' => 'He said, "You will not receive food that is provided to you except that I will inform you of its interpretation before it comes to you. That is from what my Lord has taught me. Indeed, I have left the religion of a people who do not believe in Allah , and they, in the Hereafter, are disbelievers.
'),
  array('id' => '1639','chapter_number' => '12','verse_number' => '43','content' => 'And [subsequently] the king said, "Indeed, I have seen [in a dream] seven fat cows being eaten by seven [that were] lean, and seven green spikes [of grain] and others [that were] dry. O eminent ones, explain to me my vision, if you should interpret visions."
'),
  array('id' => '1681','chapter_number' => '12','verse_number' => '85','content' => 'They said, "By Allah , you will not cease remembering Joseph until you become fatally ill or become of those who perish."
'),
  array('id' => '1735','chapter_number' => '13','verse_number' => '28','content' => 'Those who have believed and whose hearts are assured by the remembrance of Allah . Unquestionably, by the remembrance of Allah hearts are assured."
'),
  array('id' => '1743','chapter_number' => '13','verse_number' => '36','content' => 'And [the believers among] those to whom We have given the [previous] Scripture rejoice at what has been revealed to you, [O Muhammad], but among the [opposing] factions are those who deny part of it. Say, "I have only been commanded to worship Allah and not associate [anything] with Him. To Him I invite, and to Him is my return."
'),
  array('id' => '1747','chapter_number' => '13','verse_number' => '40','content' => 'And whether We show you part of what We promise them or take you in death, upon you is only the [duty of] notification, and upon Us is the account.
'),
  array('id' => '1841','chapter_number' => '15','verse_number' => '39','content' => '[Iblees] said, "My Lord, because You have put me in error, I will surely make [disobedience] attractive to them on earth, and I will mislead them all
'),
  array('id' => '1863','chapter_number' => '15','verse_number' => '61','content' => 'And when the messengers came to the family of Lot,
'),
  array('id' => '1869','chapter_number' => '15','verse_number' => '67','content' => 'And the people of the city came rejoicing.
'),
  array('id' => '1922','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '21','content' => 'They are, [in fact], dead, not alive, and they do not perceive when they will be resurrected.
'),
  array('id' => '1933','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '32','content' => 'The ones whom the angels take in death, [being] good and pure; [the angels] will say, "Peace be upon you. Enter Paradise for what you used to do."
'),
  array('id' => '1934','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '33','content' => 'Do the disbelievers await [anything] except that the angels should come to them or there comes the command of your Lord? Thus did those do before them. And Allah wronged them not, but they had been wronging themselves.
'),
  array('id' => '1935','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '34','content' => 'So they were struck by the evil consequences of what they did and were enveloped by what they used to ridicule.
'),
  array('id' => '1962','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '61','content' => 'And if Allah were to impose blame on the people for their wrongdoing, He would not have left upon the earth any creature, but He defers them for a specified term. And when their term has come, they will not remain behind an hour, nor will they precede [it].
'),
  array('id' => '1971','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '70','content' => 'And Allah created you; then He will take you in death. And among you is he who is reversed to the most decrepit [old] age so that he will not know, after [having had] knowledge, a thing. Indeed, Allah is Knowing and Competent.
'),
  array('id' => '1986','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '85','content' => 'And when those who wronged see the punishment, it will not be lightened for them, nor will they be reprieved.
'),
  array('id' => '2000','chapter_number' => '16','verse_number' => '99','content' => 'Indeed, there is for him no authority over those who have believed and rely upon their Lord.
'),
  array('id' => '2046','chapter_number' => '17','verse_number' => '17','content' => 'And how many have We destroyed from the generations after Noah. And sufficient is your Lord, concerning the sins of His servants, as Acquainted and Seeing.
'),
  array('id' => '2070','chapter_number' => '17','verse_number' => '41','content' => 'And We have certainly diversified [the contents] in this Qur\'an that mankind may be reminded, but it does not increase the disbelievers except in aversion.
'),
  array('id' => '2080','chapter_number' => '17','verse_number' => '51','content' => 'Or [any] creation of that which is great within your breasts." And they will say, "Who will restore us?" Say, "He who brought you forth the first time." Then they will nod their heads toward you and say, "When is that?" Say, "Perhaps it will be soon -
'),
  array('id' => '2086','chapter_number' => '17','verse_number' => '57','content' => 'Those whom they invoke seek means of access to their Lord, [striving as to] which of them would be nearest, and they hope for His mercy and fear His punishment. Indeed, the punishment of your Lord is ever feared.
'),
  array('id' => '2093','chapter_number' => '17','verse_number' => '64','content' => 'And incite [to senselessness] whoever you can among them with your voice and assault them with your horses and foot soldiers and become a partner in their wealth and their children and promise them." But Satan does not promise them except delusion.
'),
  array('id' => '2109','chapter_number' => '17','verse_number' => '80','content' => 'And say, "My Lord, cause me to enter a sound entrance and to exit a sound exit and grant me from Yourself a supporting authority."
'),
  array('id' => '2164','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '24','content' => 'Except [when adding], "If Allah wills." And remember your Lord when you forget [it] and say, "Perhaps my Lord will guide me to what is nearer than this to right conduct."
'),
  array('id' => '2165','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '25','content' => 'And they remained in their cave for three hundred years and exceeded by nine.
'),
  array('id' => '2175','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '35','content' => 'And he entered his garden while he was unjust to himself. He said, "I do not think that this will perish - ever.
'),
  array('id' => '2196','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '56','content' => 'And We send not the messengers except as bringers of good tidings and warners. And those who disbelieve dispute by [using] falsehood to [attempt to] invalidate thereby the truth and have taken My verses, and that of which they are warned, in ridicule.
'),
  array('id' => '2206','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '66','content' => 'Moses said to him, "May I follow you on [the condition] that you teach me from what you have been taught of sound judgement?"
'),
  array('id' => '2209','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '69','content' => '[Moses] said, "You will find me, if Allah wills, patient, and I will not disobey you in [any] order."
'),
  array('id' => '2236','chapter_number' => '18','verse_number' => '96','content' => 'Bring me sheets of iron" - until, when he had leveled [them] between the two mountain walls, he said, "Blow [with bellows]," until when he had made it [like] fire, he said, "Bring me, that I may pour over it molten copper."
'),
  array('id' => '2258','chapter_number' => '19','verse_number' => '8','content' => 'He said, "My Lord, how will I have a boy when my wife has been barren and I have reached extreme old age?"
'),
  array('id' => '2272','chapter_number' => '19','verse_number' => '22','content' => 'So she conceived him, and she withdrew with him to a remote place.
'),
  array('id' => '2304','chapter_number' => '19','verse_number' => '54','content' => 'And mention in the Book, Ishmael. Indeed, he was true to his promise, and he was a messenger and a prophet.
'),
  array('id' => '2314','chapter_number' => '19','verse_number' => '64','content' => '[Gabriel said], "And we [angels] descend not except by the order of your Lord. To Him belongs that before us and that behind us and what is in between. And never is your Lord forgetful -
'),
  array('id' => '2364','chapter_number' => '20','verse_number' => '16','content' => 'So do not let one avert you from it who does not believe in it and follows his desire, for you [then] would perish.
'),
  array('id' => '2372','chapter_number' => '20','verse_number' => '24','content' => 'Go to Pharaoh. Indeed, he has transgressed."
'),
  array('id' => '2379','chapter_number' => '20','verse_number' => '31','content' => 'Increase through him my strength
'),
  array('id' => '2385','chapter_number' => '20','verse_number' => '37','content' => 'And We had already conferred favor upon you another time,
'),
  array('id' => '2441','chapter_number' => '20','verse_number' => '93','content' => 'From following me? Then have you disobeyed my order?"
'),
  array('id' => '2488','chapter_number' => '21','verse_number' => '5','content' => 'But they say, "[The revelation is but] a mixture of false dreams; rather, he has invented it; rather, he is a poet. So let him bring us a sign just as the previous [messengers] were sent [with miracles]."
'),
  array('id' => '2489','chapter_number' => '21','verse_number' => '6','content' => 'Not a [single] city which We destroyed believed before them, so will they believe?
'),
  array('id' => '2519','chapter_number' => '21','verse_number' => '36','content' => 'And when those who disbelieve see you, [O Muhammad], they take you not except in ridicule, [saying], "Is this the one who insults your gods?" And they are, at the mention of the Most Merciful, disbelievers.
'),
  array('id' => '2615','chapter_number' => '22','verse_number' => '20','content' => 'By which is melted that within their bellies and [their] skins.
'),
  array('id' => '2630','chapter_number' => '22','verse_number' => '35','content' => 'Who, when Allah is mentioned, their hearts are fearful, and [to] the patient over what has afflicted them, and the establishers of prayer and those who spend from what We have provided them.
'),
  array('id' => '2639','chapter_number' => '22','verse_number' => '44','content' => 'And the inhabitants of Madyan. And Moses was denied, so I prolonged enjoyment for the disbelievers; then I seized them, and how [terrible] was My reproach.
'),
  array('id' => '2681','chapter_number' => '23','verse_number' => '8','content' => 'And they who are to their trusts and their promises attentive
'),
  array('id' => '2783','chapter_number' => '23','verse_number' => '110','content' => 'But you took them in mockery to the point that they made you forget My remembrance, and you used to laugh at them.
'),
  array('id' => '2793','chapter_number' => '24','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'The [unmarried] woman or [unmarried] man found guilty of sexual intercourse - lash each one of them with a hundred lashes, and do not be taken by pity for them in the religion of Allah , if you should believe in Allah and the Last Day. And let a group of the believers witness their punishment.
'),
  array('id' => '2827','chapter_number' => '24','verse_number' => '36','content' => '[Such niches are] in mosques which Allah has ordered to be raised and that His name be mentioned therein; exalting Him within them in the morning and the evenings
'),
  array('id' => '2839','chapter_number' => '24','verse_number' => '48','content' => 'And when they are called to [the words of] Allah and His Messenger to judge between them, at once a party of them turns aside [in refusal].
'),
  array('id' => '2857','chapter_number' => '25','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'He to whom belongs the dominion of the heavens and the earth and who has not taken a son and has not had a partner in dominion and has created each thing and determined it with [precise] determination.
'),
  array('id' => '2937','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '5','content' => 'And no revelation comes to them anew from the Most Merciful except that they turn away from it.
'),
  array('id' => '2941','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '9','content' => 'And indeed, your Lord - He is the Exalted in Might, the Merciful.
'),
  array('id' => '3060','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '128','content' => 'Do you construct on every elevation a sign, amusing yourselves,
'),
  array('id' => '3074','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '142','content' => 'When their brother Salih said to them, "Will you not fear Allah ?
'),
  array('id' => '3086','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '154','content' => 'You are but a man like ourselves, so bring a sign, if you should be of the truthful."
'),
  array('id' => '3094','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '162','content' => 'Indeed, I am to you a trustworthy messenger.
'),
  array('id' => '3126','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '194','content' => 'Upon your heart, [O Muhammad] - that you may be of the warners -
'),
  array('id' => '3141','chapter_number' => '26','verse_number' => '209','content' => 'As a reminder; and never have We been unjust.
'),
  array('id' => '3169','chapter_number' => '27','verse_number' => '10','content' => 'And [he was told], "Throw down your staff." But when he saw it writhing as if it were a snake, he turned in flight and did not return. [ Allah said], "O Moses, fear not. Indeed, in My presence the messengers do not fear.
'),
  array('id' => '3173','chapter_number' => '27','verse_number' => '14','content' => 'And they rejected them, while their [inner] selves were convinced thereof, out of injustice and haughtiness. So see how was the end of the corrupters.
'),
  array('id' => '3183','chapter_number' => '27','verse_number' => '24','content' => 'I found her and her people prostrating to the sun instead of Allah , and Satan has made their deeds pleasing to them and averted them from [His] way, so they are not guided,
'),
  array('id' => '3290','chapter_number' => '28','verse_number' => '38','content' => 'And Pharaoh said, "O eminent ones, I have not known you to have a god other than me. Then ignite for me, O Haman, [a fire] upon the clay and make for me a tower that I may look at the God of Moses. And indeed, I do think he is among the liars."
'),
  array('id' => '3293','chapter_number' => '28','verse_number' => '41','content' => 'And We made them leaders inviting to the Fire, and on the Day of Resurrection they will not be helped.
'),
  array('id' => '3346','chapter_number' => '29','verse_number' => '6','content' => 'And whoever strives only strives for [the benefit of] himself. Indeed, Allah is free from need of the worlds.
'),
  array('id' => '3353','chapter_number' => '29','verse_number' => '13','content' => 'But they will surely carry their [own] burdens and [other] burdens along with their burdens, and they will surely be questioned on the Day of Resurrection about what they used to invent.
'),
  array('id' => '3412','chapter_number' => '30','verse_number' => '3','content' => 'In the nearest land. But they, after their defeat, will overcome.
'),
  array('id' => '3431','chapter_number' => '30','verse_number' => '22','content' => 'And of His signs is the creation of the heavens and the earth and the diversity of your languages and your colors. Indeed in that are signs for those of knowledge.
'),
  array('id' => '3457','chapter_number' => '30','verse_number' => '48','content' => 'It is Allah who sends the winds, and they stir the clouds and spread them in the sky however He wills, and He makes them fragments so you see the rain emerge from within them. And when He causes it to fall upon whom He wills of His servants, immediately they rejoice
'),
  array('id' => '3480','chapter_number' => '31','verse_number' => '11','content' => 'This is the creation of Allah . So show Me what those other than Him have created. Rather, the wrongdoers are in clear error.
'),
  array('id' => '3529','chapter_number' => '32','verse_number' => '26','content' => 'Has it not become clear to them how many generations We destroyed before them, [as] they walk among their dwellings? Indeed in that are signs; then do they not hear?
'),
  array('id' => '3532','chapter_number' => '32','verse_number' => '29','content' => 'Say, [O Muhammad], "On the Day of Conquest the belief of those who had disbelieved will not benefit them, nor will they be reprieved."
'),
  array('id' => '3581','chapter_number' => '33','verse_number' => '48','content' => 'And do not obey the disbelievers and the hypocrites but do not harm them, and rely upon Allah . And sufficient is Allah as Disposer of affairs.
'),
  array('id' => '3591','chapter_number' => '33','verse_number' => '58','content' => 'And those who harm believing men and believing women for [something] other than what they have earned have certainly born upon themselves a slander and manifest sin.
'),
  array('id' => '3597','chapter_number' => '33','verse_number' => '64','content' => 'Indeed, Allah has cursed the disbelievers and prepared for them a Blaze.
'),
  array('id' => '3670','chapter_number' => '35','verse_number' => '10','content' => 'Whoever desires honor [through power] - then to Allah belongs all honor. To Him ascends good speech, and righteous work raises it. But they who plot evil deeds will have a severe punishment, and the plotting of those - it will perish.
'),
  array('id' => '3695','chapter_number' => '35','verse_number' => '35','content' => 'He who has settled us in the home of duration out of His bounty. There touches us not in it any fatigue, and there touches us not in it weariness [of mind]."
'),
  array('id' => '3711','chapter_number' => '36','verse_number' => '6','content' => 'That you may warn a people whose forefathers were not warned, so they are unaware.
'),
  array('id' => '3730','chapter_number' => '36','verse_number' => '25','content' => 'Indeed, I have believed in your Lord, so listen to me."
'),
  array('id' => '3750','chapter_number' => '36','verse_number' => '45','content' => 'But when it is said to them, "Beware of what is before you and what is behind you; perhaps you will receive mercy... "
'),
  array('id' => '3784','chapter_number' => '36','verse_number' => '79','content' => 'Say, "He will give them life who produced them the first time; and He is, of all creation, Knowing."
'),
  array('id' => '3792','chapter_number' => '37','verse_number' => '4','content' => 'Indeed, your God is One,
'),
  array('id' => '3872','chapter_number' => '37','verse_number' => '84','content' => 'When he came to his Lord with a sound heart
'),
  array('id' => '3908','chapter_number' => '37','verse_number' => '120','content' => '"Peace upon Moses and Aaron."
'),
  array('id' => '3928','chapter_number' => '37','verse_number' => '140','content' => '[Mention] when he ran away to the laden ship.
'),
  array('id' => '4066','chapter_number' => '39','verse_number' => '8','content' => 'And when adversity touches man, he calls upon his Lord, turning to Him [alone]; then when He bestows on him a favor from Himself, he forgets Him whom he called upon before, and he attributes to Allah equals to mislead [people] from His way. Say, "Enjoy your disbelief for a little; indeed, you are of the companions of the Fire."
'),
  array('id' => '4078','chapter_number' => '39','verse_number' => '20','content' => 'But those who have feared their Lord - for them are chambers, above them chambers built high, beneath which rivers flow. [This is] the promise of Allah . Allah does not fail in [His] promise.
'),
  array('id' => '4098','chapter_number' => '39','verse_number' => '40','content' => 'To whom will come a torment disgracing him and on whom will descend an enduring punishment."
'),
  array('id' => '4105','chapter_number' => '39','verse_number' => '47','content' => 'And if those who did wrong had all that is in the earth entirely and the like of it with it, they would [attempt to] ransom themselves thereby from the worst of the punishment on the Day of Resurrection. And there will appear to them from Allah that which they had not taken into account.
'),
  array('id' => '4113','chapter_number' => '39','verse_number' => '55','content' => 'And follow the best of what was revealed to you from your Lord before the punishment comes upon you suddenly while you do not perceive,
'),
  array('id' => '4132','chapter_number' => '39','verse_number' => '74','content' => 'And they will say, "Praise to Allah , who has fulfilled for us His promise and made us inherit the earth [so] we may settle in Paradise wherever we will. And excellent is the reward of [righteous] workers."
'),
  array('id' => '4150','chapter_number' => '40','verse_number' => '17','content' => 'This Day every soul will be recompensed for what it earned. No injustice today! Indeed, Allah is swift in account.
'),
  array('id' => '4151','chapter_number' => '40','verse_number' => '18','content' => 'And warn them, [O Muhammad], of the Approaching Day, when hearts are at the throats, filled [with distress]. For the wrongdoers there will be no devoted friend and no intercessor [who is] obeyed.
'),
  array('id' => '4185','chapter_number' => '40','verse_number' => '52','content' => 'The Day their excuse will not benefit the wrongdoers, and they will have the curse, and they will have the worst home.
'),
  array('id' => '4202','chapter_number' => '40','verse_number' => '69','content' => 'Do you not consider those who dispute concerning the signs of Allah - how are they averted?
'),
  array('id' => '4204','chapter_number' => '40','verse_number' => '71','content' => 'When the shackles are around their necks and the chains; they will be dragged
'),
  array('id' => '4258','chapter_number' => '41','verse_number' => '40','content' => 'Indeed, those who inject deviation into Our verses are not concealed from Us. So, is he who is cast into the Fire better or he who comes secure on the Day of Resurrection? Do whatever you will; indeed, He is Seeing of what you do.
'),
  array('id' => '4302','chapter_number' => '42','verse_number' => '30','content' => 'And whatever strikes you of disaster - it is for what your hands have earned; but He pardons much.
'),
  array('id' => '4312','chapter_number' => '42','verse_number' => '40','content' => 'And the retribution for an evil act is an evil one like it, but whoever pardons and makes reconciliation - his reward is [due] from Allah . Indeed, He does not like wrongdoers.
'),
  array('id' => '4348','chapter_number' => '43','verse_number' => '23','content' => 'And similarly, We did not send before you any warner into a city except that its affluent said, "Indeed, we found our fathers upon a religion, and we are, in their footsteps, following."
'),
  array('id' => '4355','chapter_number' => '43','verse_number' => '30','content' => 'But when the truth came to them, they said, "This is magic, and indeed we are, concerning it, disbelievers."
'),
  array('id' => '4477','chapter_number' => '45','verse_number' => '4','content' => 'And in the creation of yourselves and what He disperses of moving creatures are signs for people who are certain [in faith].
'),
  array('id' => '4481','chapter_number' => '45','verse_number' => '8','content' => 'Who hears the verses of Allah recited to him, then persists arrogantly as if he had not heard them. So give him tidings of a painful punishment.
'),
  array('id' => '4482','chapter_number' => '45','verse_number' => '9','content' => 'And when he knows anything of Our verses, he takes them in ridicule. Those will have a humiliating punishment.
'),
  array('id' => '4521','chapter_number' => '46','verse_number' => '11','content' => 'And those who disbelieve say of those who believe, "If it had [truly] been good, they would not have preceded us to it." And when they are not guided by it, they will say, "This is an ancient falsehood."
'),
  array('id' => '4559','chapter_number' => '47','verse_number' => '14','content' => 'So is he who is on clear evidence from his Lord like him to whom the evil of his work has been made attractive and they follow their [own] desires?
'),
  array('id' => '4594','chapter_number' => '48','verse_number' => '11','content' => 'Those who remained behind of the bedouins will say to you, "Our properties and our families occupied us, so ask forgiveness for us." They say with their tongues what is not within their hearts. Say, "Then who could prevent Allah at all if He intended for you harm or intended for you benefit? Rather, ever is Allah , with what you do, Acquainted.
'),
  array('id' => '4752','chapter_number' => '52','verse_number' => '17','content' => 'Indeed, the righteous will be in gardens and pleasure,
'),
  array('id' => '4779','chapter_number' => '52','verse_number' => '44','content' => 'And if they were to see a fragment from the sky falling, they would say, "[It is merely] clouds heaped up."
'),
  array('id' => '4932','chapter_number' => '55','verse_number' => '31','content' => 'We will attend to you, O prominent beings.
'),
  array('id' => '4954','chapter_number' => '55','verse_number' => '53','content' => 'So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?
'),
  array('id' => '4962','chapter_number' => '55','verse_number' => '61','content' => 'So which of the favors of your Lord would you deny?
'),
  array('id' => '5024','chapter_number' => '56','verse_number' => '45','content' => 'Indeed they were, before that, indulging in affluence,
'),
  array('id' => '5079','chapter_number' => '57','verse_number' => '4','content' => 'It is He who created the heavens and earth in six days and then established Himself above the Throne. He knows what penetrates into the earth and what emerges from it and what descends from the heaven and what ascends therein; and He is with you wherever you are. And Allah , of what you do, is Seeing.
'),
  array('id' => '5086','chapter_number' => '57','verse_number' => '11','content' => 'Who is it that would loan Allah a goodly loan so He will multiply it for him and he will have a noble reward?
'),
  array('id' => '5088','chapter_number' => '57','verse_number' => '13','content' => 'On the [same] Day the hypocrite men and hypocrite women will say to those who believed, "Wait for us that we may acquire some of your light." It will be said, "Go back behind you and seek light." And a wall will be placed between them with a door, its interior containing mercy, but on the outside of it is torment.
'),
  array('id' => '5112','chapter_number' => '58','verse_number' => '8','content' => 'Have you not considered those who were forbidden from private conversation, then they return to that which they were forbidden and converse among themselves about sin and aggression and disobedience to the Messenger? And when they come to you, they greet you with that [word] by which Allah does not greet you and say among themselves, "Why does Allah not punish us for what we say?" Sufficient for them is Hell, which they will [enter to] burn, and wretched is the destination.
'),
  array('id' => '5150','chapter_number' => '59','verse_number' => '24','content' => 'He is Allah , the Creator, the Inventor, the Fashioner; to Him belong the best names. Whatever is in the heavens and earth is exalting Him. And He is the Exalted in Might, the Wise.
'),
  array('id' => '5167','chapter_number' => '61','verse_number' => '4','content' => 'Indeed, Allah loves those who fight in His cause in a row as though they are a [single] structure joined firmly.
'),
  array('id' => '5235','chapter_number' => '66','verse_number' => '6','content' => 'O you who have believed, protect yourselves and your families from a Fire whose fuel is people and stones, over which are [appointed] angels, harsh and severe; they do not disobey Allah in what He commands them but do what they are commanded.
'),
  array('id' => '5244','chapter_number' => '67','verse_number' => '3','content' => '[And] who created seven heavens in layers. You do not see in the creation of the Most Merciful any inconsistency. So return [your] vision [to the sky]; do you see any breaks?
'),
  array('id' => '5300','chapter_number' => '68','verse_number' => '29','content' => 'They said, "Exalted is our Lord! Indeed, we were wrongdoers."
'),
  array('id' => '5419','chapter_number' => '70','verse_number' => '44','content' => 'Their eyes humbled, humiliation will cover them. That is the Day which they had been promised.
'),
  array('id' => '5426','chapter_number' => '71','verse_number' => '7','content' => 'And indeed, every time I invited them that You may forgive them, they put their fingers in their ears, covered themselves with their garments, persisted, and were arrogant with [great] arrogance.
'),
  array('id' => '5478','chapter_number' => '73','verse_number' => '3','content' => 'Half of it - or subtract from it a little
'),
  array('id' => '5494','chapter_number' => '73','verse_number' => '19','content' => 'Indeed, this is a reminder, so whoever wills may take to his Lord a way.
'),
  array('id' => '5498','chapter_number' => '74','verse_number' => '3','content' => 'And your Lord glorify
'),
  array('id' => '5510','chapter_number' => '74','verse_number' => '15','content' => 'Then he desires that I should add more.
'),
  array('id' => '5515','chapter_number' => '74','verse_number' => '20','content' => 'Then may he be destroyed [for] how he deliberated.
'),
  array('id' => '5524','chapter_number' => '74','verse_number' => '29','content' => 'Blackening the skins.
'),
  array('id' => '5530','chapter_number' => '74','verse_number' => '35','content' => 'Indeed, the Fire is of the greatest [afflictions]
'),
  array('id' => '5600','chapter_number' => '76','verse_number' => '9','content' => '[Saying], "We feed you only for the countenance of Allah . We wish not from you reward or gratitude.
'),
  array('id' => '5617','chapter_number' => '76','verse_number' => '26','content' => 'And during the night prostrate to Him and exalt Him a long [part of the] night.
'),
  array('id' => '5621','chapter_number' => '76','verse_number' => '30','content' => 'And you do not will except that Allah wills. Indeed, Allah is ever Knowing and Wise.
'),
  array('id' => '5654','chapter_number' => '77','verse_number' => '32','content' => 'Indeed, it throws sparks [as huge] as a fortress,
'),
  array('id' => '5703','chapter_number' => '78','verse_number' => '31','content' => 'Indeed, for the righteous is attainment -
'),
  array('id' => '5708','chapter_number' => '78','verse_number' => '36','content' => '[As] reward from your Lord, [a generous] gift [made due by] account,
'),
  array('id' => '5714','chapter_number' => '79','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'And [by] those who remove with ease
'),
  array('id' => '5776','chapter_number' => '80','verse_number' => '18','content' => 'From what substance did He create him?
'),
  array('id' => '5802','chapter_number' => '81','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'And when the stars fall, dispersing,
'),
  array('id' => '5809','chapter_number' => '81','verse_number' => '9','content' => 'For what sin she was killed
'),
  array('id' => '5819','chapter_number' => '81','verse_number' => '19','content' => '[That] indeed, the Qur\'an is a word [conveyed by] a noble messenger
'),
  array('id' => '5823','chapter_number' => '81','verse_number' => '23','content' => 'And he has already seen Gabriel in the clear horizon.
'),
  array('id' => '5884','chapter_number' => '83','verse_number' => '36','content' => 'Have the disbelievers [not] been rewarded [this Day] for what they used to do?
'),
  array('id' => '5895','chapter_number' => '84','verse_number' => '11','content' => 'He will cry out for destruction
'),
  array('id' => '5998','chapter_number' => '89','verse_number' => '5','content' => 'Is there [not] in [all] that an oath [sufficient] for one of perception?
'),
  array('id' => '6011','chapter_number' => '89','verse_number' => '18','content' => 'And you do not encourage one another to feed the poor.
'),
  array('id' => '6021','chapter_number' => '89','verse_number' => '28','content' => 'Return to your Lord, well-pleased and pleasing [to Him],
'),
  array('id' => '6113','chapter_number' => '96','verse_number' => '7','content' => 'Because he sees himself self-sufficient.
'),
  array('id' => '6138','chapter_number' => '98','verse_number' => '8','content' => 'Their reward with Allah will be gardens of perpetual residence beneath which rivers flow, wherein they will abide forever, Allah being pleased with them and they with Him. That is for whoever has feared his Lord.
'),
  array('id' => '6169','chapter_number' => '102','verse_number' => '1','content' => 'Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you
'),
  array('id' => '6190','chapter_number' => '105','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'Did He not make their plan into misguidance?
'),
  array('id' => '6218','chapter_number' => '111','verse_number' => '2','content' => 'His wealth will not avail him or that which he gained.
')
);
